text: Protonarthron indistinctum is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1938. It is known from the Democratic Republic of the Congo.BioLib.cz - Protonarthron indistinctum. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1938
